nodes.text: Bungo n' Rusti Join the Rebellion?!! Part II

Bungo n' Rusti Join the Rebellion?!! Part II was one of the canceled Bungo n' Rusti comics by James Anderson. In the story, Bungo Bung and Rusti were to have been forced into joining the Rebellion after Nien Nunb takes their cargo. It was a continuation of Bungo n' Rusti Join the Rebellion?!! Part I.
